<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1865-04-29T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1865-04-29T00:00:00-05:00" n="309" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d309">
                    <head>Merchants, Brokers, and others of Cardiff</head>
                    <p rend="flushleft">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Charles Edward Burch</hi>, <lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Consul for the United States of America at Cardiff:</hi>
                    </p>
                    <p>We, the undersigned, the merchants, brokers, and others at this port, beg to
                        convey to you our sympathy, indignation, and horror at the assassination of
                        Mr. Lincoln, the President of the United States. We feel that his loss will
                        be deplored not only by the British nation, but throughout the civilized
                        world, and we sincerely trust and believe that the great nation you
                        represent will be able to bear with dignity, and that its future progress
                        will in no way be impeded by, the great and irreparable loss it has
                        sustained.</p>
                    <closer>
                        <dateline rendition="#left">Dated this <date calendar="gregorian" when="1865-04-29">29th day of April, 1865</date>.</dateline>
                        <signed>
                            <list>
                                <item>JOHN PRIDE, <hi rend="italic">Mayor</hi>.</item>
                                <item>WILLIAM ALEXANDER, <hi rend="italic">Alderman and Justice of
                                        the Peace</hi>.</item>
                                <item>D. HOWELL, <hi rend="italic">Treasurer of St. John’s,
                                        Cardiff</hi>.</item>
                                <item>SAMUEL NASH.</item>
                                <item>SYDNEY D. JENKINS.</item>
                                <item>THOS. HODGE.</item>
                                <item>JOHN WILLIAMS.</item>
                                <item>JOSEPH ELLIOTT.</item>
                                <item>J. H. WILSON.</item>
                                <item>And some fifty others.</item>
                            </list>
                        </signed>
                    </closer>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>